subject: Tennis
lead_paragraph: Lindsay Davenport advanced to the quarterfinals of the China Open in Beijing yesterday by defeating Eleni Daniilidou, 7-5 6-3. Davenport will play fourth-seeded Elena Dementieva, who cruised past Tamira Paszek, 6-2, 6-0.Second-seed Jelena Jankovic routed Virginia Ruano Pascual, 6-0, 6-0, to set up a quarterfinal match with Akiko Morigami.Jankovic, ranked No. 3, is aiming for her fifth title this year. Top-seeded Svetlana Kuznetsova withdrew before her first match with a stomach injury.Davenport is making a comeback after giving birth to her first child in June. She won a singles title in Indonesia last week after not playing competitive tennis for almost a year.
